Spec: Continuation Lines

Purpose:
  Verify bullet continuation behavior: lines deeper than the base indent are
  joined to the previous bullet with a single space.

Must:
  This is bullet one
    with a single continuation.
  This is bullet two
    with a continuation
    and another continuation.
  This is bullet three.
  This is bullet four
      with a deeply-indented continuation.

Must not:
  Lose the indentation pattern.
  Collapse multiple bullets into one.
